
  Slowpoke    Water Type Pokémon

  Incredibly slow and dopey.  
  It takes 5 seconds for it to 
  feel pain when under attack. 
  
	Evolution Chain
      Slowpoke ► Slowbro

Stage 2 Forms:
  slowbro
  slowking

